parameters: And on this day, my fate took a drastic turn...
Umi: "Why have you brought me to such a place?"
Banka: "Well, you'll understand once you see."
Umi: "Huh? Everyone from the village⁉ Why are there so many⁉"
Banka: "Who knows... but it's certain they came here on their own..."

Shif: "Hahahaha‼ Long time no see... Priestess of Kuseshirei... Even a
barbarian like you seems to have a memory."

Shif: "Hahahaha‼ I knew you'd say that! Why? That's irrelevant! What's
important is what's going to happen from now on!"
Umi: "Everyone‼ Stop‼ What are you doing⁉"
Shif: "Hahahaha‼ Don't stop them! They all wish to die‼"
Umi: "That can't be true‼ You‼ You're the one controlling them‼"

Shif: "Oh! You figured it out. It's all due to my hypnotic magic. I commend
you."

Shif: "Careful with your words... These barbarians will commit suicide or
set the village ablaze with just one whim of mine. Of course, I could also
have them attack you right here and now."

Shif: "And of course, that includes your foolish husband sleeping at
home..."
Umi: "What⁉ Don't lay a finger on Kru‼"

Shif: "That depends on your decision. If you can't listen to me, you know
very well what will happen, don't you?"
Shif: "Could it be... you don't understand?"
Umi: "I'll listen to what you say... so please..."
Umi: "So please... don't harm the villagers."

Shif: "Don't harm? That's how you feel. A mere wish. What do you want me to
do?"

Shif: "Please? Hmm... You really don't know how to ask for something, do
you?"
Shif: "Kukukuku... In exchange for that... Umi will...?"
Umi: "In exchange for that... Umi will..."
Umi: "Uu... I'll do anything you say!"

Shif: "Hahahahaha!! It's a deal!! That's right! If you ask like that, I
might just listen to your request! Hahahahaha!"
Banka: "We did it, Lord Shif... It was worth hiding for a whole year!"
Shif: "Indeed... It took quite some time to deepen the hypnosis."
Umi: "Damn it... Banka... you betrayed us..."

Banka: "The ones who betrayed were the villagers... preferring that
outsider over me."

Shif: "Well, Banka. That's fine. They are your villagers now. Do with them
as you please."

Shif: "Now, the time for the contract has come... Woman, get up on that
platform..."
Shif: "Why... such things don't matter... Hurry up and get on."

Shif: "Oh great Kusechirei! Here we have the contractor, the jewel, and the
shrine maiden gathered...!"

Shif: "With this moment, the contract is established! Awaken from your long
dark slumber and let your blood rush with the joy of flesh!"
The contract is established... what is going to happen to me...
Shif: "We shall now commence the rite of reincarnation through conception!"

Shif: "Now... woman... your body belongs to Lord Kusechirei. From now on,
you shall dedicate yourself to him."
Umi: "Lord Kusechirei's? What do you mean..."

Shif: "Your pussy has become the sperm sac for Lord Kusechirei to incarnate
and return. And the sperm that will impregnate you is mine."
Umi: "Eh? Eh? What do you mean... what in the world..."

Shif: "Fufufu... It's natural to be confused. But before the reincarnation
through conception, I must train your body to the marrow of your bones..."
Umi (This is strange... my core is hot... and it's tingling somehow...)

Shif: "Hooh... The effects are already showing, are they? It seems... you
were quite the lewd one from the start..."

Umi (This is strange... so strange... what should I do... what's happening
to Umi's body...)
Shif: "Hahahahahaha! I'm looking forward to what comes next!"
The sudden turn of events had my mind in utter chaos...

The villagers taken hostage, Shif's appearance, and then something
incomprehensible being done to me...

And the term "sperm sac"... those words were perfectly suited to foreshadow
a hopeless future for me.
I can probably never return to those warm, beloved days...
I understood that much... but I wasn't ready to accept it yet...
